headline: Carvana stock tumbles 43%, books worst day on record as bankruptcy fears rev up
content: Shares of the used-car retailer logged the worst day on record Wednesday amid growing concerns about bankruptcy.

headline: Boeing Stock Upgraded On New Order Deal Buzz, As This 50-Year Era Ends
content: Bank of America upgraded Boeing stock as the Dow aerospace giant reportedly nears a deal with UAL for dozens of 787 Dreamliner jets.
